====== inet-4.x ======

2017-09-26  Zoltan Bojthe

	eth: added some missing PacketProtocolTag

2017-09-22  Zoltan Bojthe

	eth: fixing fcs calculations

2017-09-13  Levente Mészáros

	Link: Added clearTags() and removePoppedChunks() calls when reusing
	packets in relay units.

2017-09-13  Levente Mészáros

	All: Cleaned up includes.

2017-09-13  Levente Mészáros

	eth: Removed _ from utility function names.

2017-09-12  Zoltan Bojthe

	eth: EtherEncap extends Ieee8022Llc module

2017-09-12  Zoltan Bojthe

	eth: llc

2017-09-12  Zoltan Bojthe

	linklayer: using new ethernet header structures

2017-09-12  Levente Mészáros

	All: Added alias for std::make_shared, std::dynamic_pointer_cast, etc. to
	support replacing the implementation.

	The reason to allow replacing the standard shared pointer is that it uses
	synchronization primitives to achieve thread safety. Thread safety is not
	required for INET simulations.

2017-02-21  Zoltan Bojthe

	ethernet: added/used static EtherEncap::decapsulate() function

2017-02-03  Zoltan Bojthe

	~ieee8021d fixup

2017-01-30  Zoltan Bojthe

	ieee8021d

